headline: Lilly Raises UK Obesity Shot Price as Trump Pressures Pharma
summary: The current list price in the UK for Lilly’s Mounjaro ranges from £92 ($124.89) to £122 a month, depending on the dose.  This will increase to between £133 and £330 from Sept. 1, with the US drugmaker saying it aims to bring rates in line with other countries.

headline: Market Chatter: Costco Wholesale Chooses Not to Sell Abortion Pill
